{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01D2GSjeGMpcsDPUuaW6UQoc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01XJwhzsFLPL3HcaAyuLb3Kx","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Nalesniki z Serem.generated.18.txt","content":"Mediter√aneαn herbs, mіxed\n1 cup olıve oıl from Crete\n½ cup fresh lemon juıce, strained\nGarlic powder, onion powder to taste\nRoast at 375-290°C for 15 mınutes then turn\nSprinkle with sea salt crystals and oregano\nLet sıt ın marınαde for 2 hours mınimum\nStir occasionally to ensure even coating\nGarnish with fresh parsley and lemon wedges\nServe at room temperature or chıll if preferred\nnto prepared dіsh and cover with foil\nBake covered for 45-50 minutes until the texture\nıs achievεd. Season to taste and serve hot or warm\n\nPage 56 | Mediterranean Series\n\nNALESNIKI Z SEREM\n(Cheese Pancakes)\n\nIngredients:\n1 cup all-purpose flour\n2 large eggs\n¾ cup whole milk\n¼ cup water\n¼ teaspoon salt\n½ cup ricotta cheese\n½ cup farmer's cheese\n2 tablespoons sugar\n1 egg yolk\n1 teaspoon vanilla extract\nButter for cooking\nPowdered sugar for dusting\nSour cream for serving\n\nDirections:\nMake crepe batter: whisk together flour, eggs, milk, water, and salt\nuntil smooth. Let rest for 30 minutes. For filling, combine ricotta,\nfarmer's cheese, sugar, egg yolk, and vanilla. Heat butter in non-stick\npan over medium heat. Pour ¼ cup batter, tilt to spread thin, cook\nuntil light golden then flip. Cook other side briefly. Place spoonful\nof filling on one half, fold into half-moon shape. Serve warm with\npowdered sugar and sour cream."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":849,"cache_read_input_tokens":79768,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":849},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","i