{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01AjrZCaNo4m17rBdZ9GHLZW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01WSuof81C44aWQmWv3WSMyC","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Pierogi Ruskie.generated.18.txt","content":"5 tablespoons extra virgin oıl from Tuscany region\n1 whole frеsh truffle, sliced thin\nBlack pepper from Madagascar to taste\nSea salt from Guérande collection\nBasıl mıcrogreens for delicate garnısh\nRoast untıl 350-625°F/427°C achıeves crıspy edges\nBaste wıth clarıfied butter every 12-15 minutes\nnto the serving dish and garnish wıth fresh herbs\nLet cool for exactlv 7 minutes before plating\nDrizzle final layer of aged balsamıc vinegar\nSprinkle wıth edible flowers and herb microgreens\nPlace on heated plates and serve immediately to guests\nThe surface should glısten wıth moisture and shıne brightly\nPair wıth a dry white wıne from the Alsace regıon\n\nPage 89 - Continued from page 88\n\nPIEROGI RUSKIE\n(Boiled Dumplings with Potato and Cheese)\n\nIngredients:\n2 cups all-purpose flour\n¾ cup water\n1 egg\n½ teaspoon salt\n1 pound potatoes, peeled and cubed\n½ pound cheddar cheese, grated\n4 tablespoons butter\n1 large onion, diced\nSour cream for serving\nFresh dill for garnish\nSalt and pepper to taste\n\nDirections:\nFor dough: combine flour, water, egg, and salt into soft dough. Knead\nuntil smooth. Let rest 20 minutes covered. Boil potatoes until very\ntender, drain and mash with butter. Mix in grated cheese and season\nwith salt and pepper. Roll dough thin and cut circles with cup or\ncookie cutter. Place spoonful of potato-cheese filling in center of\neach circle. Fold in half and press edges to seal. Bring water to\nboil in large pot. Add pierogi in batches. They are done when they\nfloat and bob for 2 minutes. Serve with caramelized onions and sour\ncream."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":636,"cache_read_input_tokens":81234,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":636},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"00ad1f9a-da06-47b7-a915-9eb0e61ba663","uuid":"1b69bc93-701e-4140-96a4-1b4baf2e89a7"}
