{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01WLynq3U8wX7pR7b8VYgPvz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Xop54FgiEtWPVjVVJfV97r","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Honey Glazed Ham.generated.18.txt","content":"HONEY GLAZED HAM\n\nNothing says celebration quite like a honey-glazed ham taking center stage at the holiday table.\nThis recipe draws inspiration from Southern culinary traditions, where slow-roasted ham glazed\nwith a shiny amber coating of honey, mustard, and spices becomes the main attraction of any feast.\nThe combination of sweet and savory flavors caramelizes beautifully during roasting, creating a\ncrispy exterior while keeping the interior moist and tender. Studded with cloves and basted with\nthe glaze throughout cooking, this elegant yet surprisingly simple dish never fails to impress.\n\nIngredients:\n1 fully cooked ham (8-10 pounds)\n½ cup honey\n¼ cup Dijon mustard\n2 tablespoons apple cider vinegar\n¼ cup brown sugar\n2 tablespoons butter\n1 teaspoon ground cloves\n½ teaspoon ground cinnamon\n½ teaspoon black pepper\nWhole cloves for studding\n1 cup pineapple juice or orange juice\n\nDirections:\nPreheat oven to 325°F (163°C). Place ham cut-side down in roasting pan.\nPour fruit juice into bottom of pan. Cover tightly with foil and bake\nfor 15-18 minutes per pound. Combine honey, mustard, vinegar, brown\nsugar, butter, and spices in saucepan. Heat gently over low heat until\nbutter melts and ingredients blend. Score the top of ham in diamond\npattern and stud with whole cloves. Remove foil from ham and brush\ngenerously with glaze. Continue baking uncovered for final 30 minutes,\nbasting with glaze every 8-10 minutes. Let rest 15 minutes before\ncarving and serving."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":589,"cache_read_input_tokens":82551,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":589},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"00ad1f9a-da06-47b7-a915-9eb0e61ba663","uuid":"1afc1c41-0b7e-4b6e-aea3-69e6a82da43b"}
